OL,6,FThe average delay for flights across
OL,7,Fall airports was almost 20 minutes and
OL,8,F42 seconds, down from 23 minutes and
OL,9,F12 seconds in 2022, when the aviation
OL,10,Fsector struggled to cope with a surge
OL,11,Fin demand for holidays following the
OL,12,Fend of coronavirus travel restrictions.
OL,14,FThe analysis took into account all
OL,15,Fscheduled and chartered departures
OL,16,Ffrom the 22 commercial UK airports
OL,17,Fwith at least 1,000 outbound flights
OL,18,Flast year. Cancellations were not
OL,19,Fincluded.
