OL,6,FNaomi Leach, deputy editor of consumer
OL,7,Fmagazine Which? Travel, said: "It's
OL,8,Fclear from these latest figures that
OL,9,Fmillions of passengers continued to
OL,10,Fexperience unacceptably long hold-ups
OL,11,Flast year.
OL,13,F"This cannot be allowed to become the
OL,14,Fnew normal."
OL,16,FCAA director Tim Johnson said it is
OL,17,Fvital the aviation sector "focuses on
OL,18,Fresilience" ahead of the summer
OL,19,Fholiday period to "keep passenger
OL,20,Fdisruption to a minimum".
